Underfoot, a herringbone-tread rubber outsole offers stop-and-go traction.

The upper is crafted from white textile with wavy overlays in contrasting tan and black hues. Webbing three-stripes in Wild Pine adorn the quarter panel, while Ivy Park branding is embroidered on the heel overlay. The sneaker rides on a sculpted green foam midsole, supported underfoot by a lugged Traxion rubber outsole.

results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas Super Sleek Chunky ‘Halls of Ivy’ is taken from the fifth collaborative collection with the athleisure brand co-founded by Beyoncé. This fashion-forward take on the adidas Samba features an off-white corduroy upper with tonal leather three-stripes and grey premium suede overlays. Details include mismatched Ivy Park and adidas tongue tags, a navy leather-lined interior, and coiled bungee detailing at the heel. The low-profile design up top is offset by a chunky platform sole unit with segmented sidewalls.

results.name: adidas Super Sleek Boot Beyonce Ivy Park Halls of Ivy
results.story: Launching as part of the fifth collection with Beyoncé’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas Super Sleek Boot ‘Halls of Ivy’ presents a sneaker-boot hybrid that draws inspiration from the classic Samba. A monochromatic olive green finish is applied to the upper, lined in warm Sherpa fleece and built with a blend of ballistic mesh and premium suede. Utilitarian details include D-ring eyelets and a coiled bungee strap that wraps around the high-cut collar. The towering silhouette is anchored by a gum rubber platform sole.

results.name: adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 Legacy Indigo Turbo
results.story: The adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 ‘Legacy Indigo Turbo’ showcases vibrant hues on a performance running shoe designed with direct input from world-class athletes. Made with 50% recycled content, the semi-translucent textile upper is rendered in a gradient blue finish with oversized three-stripes in a bright red hue. The cushioned midsole is composed of two layers of Lightstrike Pro foam, enhanced with a series of carbon-infused EnergyRods for limited energy loss. The outsole features grippy Continental Rubber under the forefoot and heel.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost OG Beyonce Ivy Park Solar Green
results.story: Launching as part of the fifth collaborative collection with the athleisure brand co-founded by Beyoncé, the Ivy Park x adidas UltraBoost OG ‘Halls of Ivy’ treats the running shoe to a monochrome neon green makeover. Drawcord lacing secures the flexible Primeknit upper, bolstered with a molded midfoot cage and external heel counter. Dual adidas and Ivy Park branding decorates the sockliner. The sneaker sits atop a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced underfoot by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Y-3 Qisan Cozy Black Bliss Red
results.story: The adidas Y-3 Qisan Cozy ‘Bliss Black’ debuts a lifestyle runner that blends adidas performance technology with styling inspired by the Y-3 Qasa. The slip-on features a stretchy neoprene upper with contrasting black, off-white and crimson paneling. Suede and rubberized overlays bolster the lightweight build, while dual webbing pull tabs provide easy on and off. The sneaker sits atop a stacked Lightstrike midsole, featuring a red TPU plate sandwiched between the two layers.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost OG Beyonce Ivy Park Peloton Focus Olive

The lightweight running shoe carries an olive green knit upper secured with toggle lace closure. ‘Ivy Park’ is debossed on the tonal heel counter, while the leather tongue tag displays dual adidas and Peloton branding. The sneaker rides atop a matching green Boost midsole, supported underfoot by a neon green Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 Halo Ivory Pink Solar Gold

Semi-translucent textile is utilized on the upper, marked with floating pink three-stripes on the lateral side and a ‘NYC 2021’ graphic on the opposing side. An internal fit system provides a feeling of lockdown while reducing pressure on the top of the foot. The midsole, featuring energy-returning Boost with Lightstrike cushioning, works in tandem with a full-length carbon fiber plate. A Continental Rubber outsole yields grippy traction.

Underfoot, an outsole pattern inspired by the original Chuck Taylor delivers reliable traction.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Flyease Black Wild Mango
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star CX FlyEase ‘Black Wild Mango’ brings Nike’s groundbreaking easy-entry technology to the sneaker icon. Black stretch canvas is utilized on the upper, featuring traditional lace closure and an innovative TPE heel cage that’s designed to flex and collapse, allowing wearers to step into the shoe hands-free. The heel then rebounds, locking the foot in place. The sneaker rides on a bright orange CX foam midsole, made visible through a wraparound translucent heel cage.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Flyease White Wild Mango
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star CX FlyEase ‘White Wild Mango’ overhauls the foundational sneaker with Nike’s revolutionary easy access technology. Constructed from stretch white canvas, the streamlined upper features a padded low-cut collar and a TPE heel cage that flexes, collapses, and rebounds, enabling hands-free on and off. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an orange CX foam midsole, exposed through a translucent cage that wraps around the heel.

results.name: Converse Weapon CX Joshua Vides Black Clear
results.story: The Joshua Vides x Converse Weapon CX ‘Made in Studio’ is taken from a capsule collection with the LA-based artist. Inspired by craftsmanship and process, this reworked Weapon features a black organic canvas upper with frayed edges and transparent TPU on the quarter panel and toe box. Dual Converse and Joshua Vides branding appears on the woven tongue tag and genuine cork insole. The sneaker rides on an exaggerated midsole built with injected EVA, good for lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Converse Pro Leather Joshua Vides Natural Ivory

The unique build is intended to tell the story of craftsmanship and process, highlighted by an off-white organic canvas upper secured with measuring tape laces. Digitally printed black lines resemble imperfect marker strokes, while durable TecTuff leather at the toe and heel mimics the look of black duct tape. Dual Converse and Joshua Vides branding appears on the woven tongue tag and cork insole.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Joshua Vides White

A zip-up shroud composed of white Tyvek material envelops the upper, built with black organic canvas and embellished with 3D-printed white polka dots. Black tumbled leather is utilized on the tongue and a pull tab at the heel. The high-top is mounted on an off-white rubber midsole, accented with black pinstripes and supported by a translucent rubber outsole.

Dual Converse and Golf Wang branding is stamped on the Ortholite sockliner. Anchoring the low-top is a pink-tinged translucent rubber midsole and outsole.

A die-cut One Star logo adorns the quarter panel, while dual CONS and Carhartt branding is stamped on the cushioned CX Foam insole. results.name: Converse Jack Purcell Moncler Fragment Black
results.story: Launching as part of a collaborative three-piece pack designed by Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Fragment Design x Moncler x Converse Jack Purcell ‘Black’ makes use of a 12oz canvas upper with contrast white stitching. The reinforced rubber toe cap is etched with the signature Jack Purcell ‘smile,’ while the dual-branded heel strip displays Moncler’s ‘M’ logo and Fragment’s lightning bolt emblem. The low-top is mounted on a white rubber midsole, featuring ‘Moncler/Fragment’ printed in block lettering across the lateral sidewall.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70s Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Grey
results.story: The Comme des Garçons PLAY x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Steel Gray’ highlights neutral tones on Rei Kawakubo’s reimagined Chuck. The grey canvas upper is decorated on the lateral side with an oversized heart and eyes logo in simple black and white. The icon is repeated in red atop the dual-branded Ortholite sockliner, good for lightweight cushioning with each step. The high-top is mounted on an Egret-colored rubber midsole, reinforced underfoot by a diamond-traction rubber outsole in a traditional brown finish.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Blue
results.story: The Comme des Garçons PLAY x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Blue Quartz’ features a traditional canvas build dominated by Filip Pagowski’s instantly familiar heart and eyes logo. On the sneaker’s lateral side, the oversized icon stands out in black and white against a royal blue backdrop. Traditional Chuck 70 components are present and accounted for, including contrast stitching, chrome eyelets, a reinforced rubber toe cap and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an Ortholite sockliner, featuring dual Converse and CDG Play branding.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Comme des Garcons PLAY Grey
results.story: The Comme des Garçons PLAY x Converse Chuck 70 Low ‘Steel Gray’ showcases the Japanese brand’s iconic heart and eyes logo in a simple black and white finish. The oversized icon is cropped on the lateral side of the upper, constructed from sturdy grey canvas with contrast stitching and a reinforced rubber toe cap. Dual Converse and CDG Play branding is stamped on the Ortholite insole. The low-top is mounted on an off-white rubber midsole, featuring the Chuck 70’s signature raised sidewalls and a tonal license plate at the heel.

results.story: Converse recrafts its original Chuck Taylor All Star from the 1970s with modern design elements that pay tribute to the brand’s history and heritage. Blending classic style with vintage-inspired details, the Chuck 70 Low Top 'Parchment' features a heavier-grade canvas upper in a timeless, natural colorway and a higher-profile rubber midsole. All Star accents like the star-centered heel patch and vulcanized rubber outsole help uphold the authentic, retro-inspired look of this classic sneaker.

results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Pink’ sneaker brings a playful touch of color to the classic high-top silhouette. The design was first introduced in 1917 as a basketball shoe, since growing to icon status. Constructed with a lightweight and durable canvas upper, the shoe’s high top offers coverage, while medial eyelets promote airflow. The classic All Star ankle patch decorates the lateral side, and the signature vulcanized rubber sole completes the look.

results.story: The New Balance 550 ‘Team Carolina Blue’ showcases a simplistic color scheme that stays true to the shoe’s late ‘80s roots. The low-top features a white leather upper with contrasting hits of powder blue throughout. They include the sneaker’s various branding elements, highlighted by a raised ‘N’ on the quarter panel and a flying NB logo on the back heel. The sneaker’s throwback tooling takes the form of a durable rubber cupsole, complete with an exposed EVA wedge on the medial sidewall.

results.story: Releasing as part of the ‘Red Label’ series, the New Balance 990v4 Made In USA ‘Grey’ continues the celebration of the brand’s iconic 990 franchise. The retro runner showcases a core grey color scheme, executed on a breathable mesh upper with pigskin suede overlays. Contrasting the neutral palette is a crimson ‘Version 4’ tag on the sneaker’s lateral side, and matching red New Balance branding on the tongue tag and back heel. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of an ENCAP midsole, featuring a soft foam core and a durable polyurethane rim.

New Balance 574 Jaden Smith Surplus Materials
results.story: Designed in partnership with the multi-talented actor and musician, the Jaden Smith x New Balance 574 ‘Surplus Materials’ delivers a uniquely sustainable take on the retro runner. No two pairs are the same, as the upper is made with 73% surplus materials, 18% virgin materials and 9% recycled content. A randomized palette is executed on a build that combines a breathable mesh base with synthetic overlays and contrast stitch detailing over the signature ‘N’ logo. The sneaker is mounted on an ENCAP midsole, featuring a soft foam core surrounded by a durable polyurethane carrier.

results.story: Created by Tinker Hatfield with direct input from LA-based dance crew the Kinjaz, the Nike Air Sesh ‘Dance’ debuts a stylish new silhouette made expressly for dancers. Adopting a familiar color palette that recalls the OG Nike Cortez, the low-top carries a white leather upper with a red leather Swoosh on the lateral side and a rear-facing Swoosh outlined in black on the medial side. A bright blue pinstripe accents the foam midsole, supported by an ultra-flexible outsole built with two different rubber compounds and branded with a glow-in-the-dark Swoosh.

results.story: The Santa Cruz x PUMA Suede ‘Shark’ channels the West Coast sensibilities of the iconic skateboarding brand. The upper is crafted from black suede with stitched Formstrips in mismatched colors: purple on the right sight of each shoe, and lime green on the left. The latter hue is repeated on the interior lining of the tongue and collar. A colorful Santa Cruz ‘Shark’ graphic decorates the TPU tongue tag and the lateral side panel. A tan rubber cupsole underpins the vintage low-top.

Reebok Zig Kinetica II The Jetstones Rosie the Robot
results.story: The Reebok Zig Kinetica 2 ‘Rosie’ is taken from the ‘Flintstones Meet Jetsons’ collection, inspired by a 1987 made-for-TV movie that united two classic Hanna-Barbera series in a cartoon crossover event. This pair mimics the look of the Jetsons’ robot maid Rosie, featuring varying shades of blue throughout a textile upper overlaid with translucent no-dew skins. A sculpted white tongue represents Rosie’s signature cap, while the robot’s model number is listed on the black webbing heel pull. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a Floatride Fuel midsole, wrapped in a solid black Zig Energy Shell for added responsiveness.

results.name: Reebok Club C Legacy The Jetsons Jane Jetson
results.story: The Reebok Club C Legacy ‘Jane Jetson’ is taken from the ‘Flintstones Meet Jetsons’ collection, inspired by a 1987 made-for-TV movie that brought together two classic Hanna-Barbera series. This pair utilizes a Brilliant Pink leather upper reminiscent of Judy Jetson’s two-piece dress. Metallic silver detailing on the eyestay, coupled with translucent rubber tooling, symbolizes The Jetsons’ futuristic milieu. Underfoot, the outsole features custom graphics that reference Jane’s beauty regimen and the robots who help her prepare.

results.name: Reebok Zig Kinetica II The Flintstones The Great Gazoo
results.story: Launching as part of the ‘Flintstones Meet Jetsons’ collection, the Reebok Zig Kinetica 2 ‘The Great Gazoo’ draws inspiration from a 1987 made-for-TV movie that merged two classic Hanna-Barbera series. Paying tribute to Fred and Barney’s extraterrestrial foil, the lifestyle runner sports a Flora Green mesh upper with protruding antennae-like eyelets. The Great Gazoo’s signature greeting — ‘Hello Dum Dum’ — is inscribed across a pair of black webbing heel pulls. A glow-in-the-dark TPU cage features the same distinctive zigzag shape that frames the Floatride Fuel midsole.

results.name: Reebok Shaqnosis The Big Aristotle
results.story: The Reebok Shaqnosis ‘Big Aristotle’ references Shaquille O’Neal’s self-imposed nickname with a unique design inspired by ancient Greek architecture. A subtle marbled finish distinguishes the off-white leather upper, featuring the shoe’s signature arcing overlays in tonal suede. An unexpected pop of color arrives via a purple suede heel tab marked with Shaq’s Dunkman logo. The mid-top rests on a lightweight EVA midsole with visible Hexalite cushioning in the heel.

Reebok Zig Kinetica II Edge Brown Green
results.story: The Reebok Zig Kinetica 2 ‘Edge’ brings subdued earth tones to a trail-inspired silhouette built for rugged terrain. Toggle lacing secures the patterned grey textile upper, reinforced with forefoot and heel overlays in tan and green. Vibrant pops of color arrive via pink contrast stitching and a pair of yellow webbing pull tabs. The sneaker is mounted on a lightly speckled Floatride Fuel midsole, supported by an anti-slip Vibram Ecostep outsole with aggressive outdoor lugs.

results.name: Reebok Club C Legacy Keith Haring Three-Eyed Smiling Face
results.story: Launching as part of a five-piece footwear collection celebrating the iconic street artist, the Keith Haring x Reebok Club C Legacy ‘Three-Eyed Smiling Face’ dresses the tennis-inspired silhouette in smooth red leather. On the lateral quarter panel, Reebok branding accompanies a graphic depicting Haring’s three-eyed smiling face. A second Reebok wordmark is stamped on the heel tab, while the artist’s signature is scrawled on the woven tongue tag and custom sockliner. The vivid scarlet hue up top is countered by a rubber cupsole in a neutral grey finish.

results.name: Reebok GL 6000 Keith Haring Pure Primary Colors
results.story: Taken from a five-piece collection inspired by the ‘80s street art icon, the Keith Haring x Reebok GL 6000 ‘Dog and Human Heel Print’ updates the retro runner with a verdant color palette. The upper is crafted from bright green nylon with contrasting white side stripes and tonal overlays in leather and suede. Keith Haring’s canine and human figures are embroidered on the back heel, while the artist’s signature is scrawled on the woven tongue tag and sockliner. Color-popped accents in yellow and orange enliven the white EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a solid black rubber outsole.

results.name: Reebok Classic Leather Legacy AZ Keith Haring Dancing Figures
results.story: The Keith Haring x Reebok Classic Leather Legacy AZ ‘Dancing Figures Heel Print’ represents one of five models that make up a limited footwear collection centered around the street art icon. The upper is constructed from white textile with blue leather side stripes and reinforced overlays in grey suede and white leather. Unique branding elements include the artist’s signature on the tongue tag and a trio of his dancing figures stamped on the suede heel tab. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a die-cut EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a cored-out black rubber outsole.

results.name: Reebok Pump Omni Zone II Juun.J White
results.story: The Juun J x Reebok Pump Omni Zone 2 ‘White Cold Grey’ is taken from a three-piece pack developed in partnership with the Korean fashion designer. Juun’s elevated take on the retro ‘90s hoops shoe features a grey premium leather upper with perforated detailing on the tox box and quarter panel. Reebok’s Pump technology combines with leather laces to a deliver a secure fit. ‘Juun J’ is embossed on an added TPU heel piece in a glossy white finish, complementing the wavy midfoot cage brought over from the original design. The sneaker rides on an EVA midsole with Hexalite cushioning, visible through a cut-out window in the rubber outsole.

results.name: Reebok Pump Omni Zone II Juun.J Brown
results.story: The Juun J x Reebok Pump Omni Zone 2 ‘Wild Brown’ is drawn from a monochromatic three-piece pack made in collaboration with the Korean designer. The vintage ‘90s hoops shoe features a premium tan leather upper with perforated detailing at the toe box and quarter panel. Leather laces combine with Reebok’s Pump technology to deliver a secure fit. The signature TPU cage is rendered in a glossy finish, matching an added TPU heel piece marked with embossed Juun J branding. The mid-top rides on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Reebok Pump Omni Zone II Juun.J Black
results.story: Launching as part of a monochromatic three-piece pack with the Korean designer, the Juun J x Reebok Pump Omni Zone 2 ‘Black’ treats the ‘90s hoops shoe to a material upgrade. The premium black leather upper is accented with perforated paneling and secured with a combination of leather laces and Reebok’s retro Pump technology. Glossy black TPU is utilized on the wavy midfoot cage and an added heel piece embossed with Juun J branding. A matching black EVA midsole is enhanced with Hexalite cushioning

results.name: Reebok Club C 85 Pleasures (2021)
results.story: Conceived in partnership with the LA-based streetwear brand, the Pleasures x Reebok Club C 85 ‘Pine Green’ outfits the retro tennis shoe in a premium build. Black Cordura textile is utilized on the upper, accented with contrast white stitching and fortified with shaggy suede overlays in a lush green hue. Pleasures branding decorates a heart-shaped logo window on the lateral quarter panel and a woven tongue tag on the right shoe. A solid black rubber cupsole packs an EVA wedge for a cushioned ride.

results.name: Reebok Club C Legacy Pleasures
results.story: The Pleasures x Reebok Club C Legacy ‘Pure Grey’ delivers a modern take on the heritage tennis model, courtesy of the LA-based streetwear label founded by Alex James. A greyscale finish permeates a layered suede upper with breathable mesh construction at the vamp and collar. Pleasures branding adorns the lateral heel, woven tongue tag and sockliner. The low-top is anchored by a translucent rubber cupsole, featuring EVA cushioning and printed text on the lateral sidewall that reads ‘Pleasures Club C Legacy.’

results.story: A triple collab shoe, the Reebok BEAMS x NEEDLES x Beatnik 'Black Purple' revives a beloved 90s outdoor sandal with a fresh twist. A raw center seam and adjustable Velcro heel strap reinforce the design, while underfoot a jagged outsole keeps the sandal firmly rooted in heritage design.

The sneaker rides on a sold white vulcanized rubber midsole, reinforced underfoot by a waffle-tread gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Vans Vault OG Old Skool LX Geoff McFetridge Ollie Patchie
results.story: Releasing as part of a capsule collection with the LA-based artist, the Geoff McFetridge x Vans Vault OG Old Skool LX ‘Ollie Patch’ carries a black canvas upper with sewn-on ripstop textile graphics in contrasting royal blue, yellow, tan and coral hues. The low-top is mounted on a solid white vulcanized rubber midsole, featuring a textured toe bumper and a crimson Off the Wall license plate at the back heel. Underfoot, a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole delivers optimal grip.

results.name: Vans Vault OG Authentic LX Geoff McFetridge Gamelan Of Tags
results.story: Launching as part of a capsule collection with the LA-based artist and illustrator, the Geoff McFetridge x Vans Vault OG Authentic LX ‘Gamelan of Tags’ features a white canvas upper covered in a multicolor patchwork design. The stitched-on panels are inspired by the artist’s personal items, including a 20-year-old tote bag and a T-shirt he wears while painting. The sneaker sits atop a solid white vulcanized rubber midsole, supported underfoot by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Vans Vault Sk8-Hi LX Geoff McFetridge Freetime
results.story: The Geoff McFetridge x Vans Vault OG Sk8-Hi LX ‘Freetime’ is drawn from an apparel and footwear collection created in partnership with the LA-based artist and illustrator. The classic high-top makes use of an indigo canvas upper with a blue leather side stripe and navy suede construction on the vamp and heel. On each side panel, large stitched-on patches display variations on McFetridge’s ‘Jump’ graphic. The sneaker is supported by vulcanized tooling that pairs a solid white midsole with a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole.

results.story: In celebration of the legacy of 19th-century post-impressionist painter Vincent van Gogh, Vans teamed up with the Van Gogh Museum to release a limited edition colorway that honors Van Gogh’s Almond Blossom (1890). The high-top features an all-over print of the painting on its canvas upper, with padding and the signature Vans white stripe on the side panels. A portion of the profits from the project were set aside for the preservation of Van Gogh’s estate.
